sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as kserve-webhook-server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>mTLS
    participant Controller as kserve-controller-manager<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant Knative as Knative Serving API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Storage as S3/GCS/Azure<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Init as storage-initializer<br/>Cloud Credentials
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Predictor as InferenceService Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as External Client<br/>Bearer Token (optional)

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Model Deployment
    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>Bearer Token (kubeconfig)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate InferenceService<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI->>Controller: InferenceService Created<br/>(watch event)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Resources<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Knative: Create Knative Service<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Knative->>K8sAPI: Create Pod with storage-initializer
    Init->>Storage: Download Model Artifacts<br/>AWS IAM/GCP SA/Azure SAS
    Storage-->>Init: Model Files
    Note over Init,Predictor: Model available on shared volume
    Predictor->>Predictor: Load Model
    Predictor-->>K8sAPI: Pod Ready

    Note over Client,Predictor: Flow 2: Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>Predictor: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS (if enabled) Istio AuthZ
    Predictor->>Predictor: Run Inference
    Predictor-->>Gateway: Prediction Result
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,Predictor: Flow 3: InferenceGraph (Multi-Step)
    Client->>Gateway: Inference Request<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    Gateway->>Router: Route to InferenceGraph<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS
    Router->>Transformer: Pre-processing<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Transformer-->>Router: Transformed Data
    Router->>Predictor: Prediction Request<br/>HTTP/8080 mTLS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Predictor-->>Router: Prediction Result
    Router-->>Gateway: Final Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Predictor,Prometheus: Flow 4: Observability
    participant Agent as kserve-agent (sidecar)
    participant CloudEvents as CloudEvents Broker
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    Predictor->>Agent: Request/Response Logs<br/>localhost HTTP
    Agent->>CloudEvents: CloudEvents<br/>8080/TCP HTTP TLS (optional)
    Prometheus->>Predictor: Scrape /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
